==English==

===Alternative spellings===
'''[[cubic centimeter]]''' (''US''; ''plural'' '''cubic centimeters''')

===Noun===
'''[[cubic]] [[centimetre]]'''  (''plural:'' '''[[cubic centimetres]]''')
# A [[unit]] of [[volume]] equal to that of a [[cube]] having sides each one [[centimetre]] in length, commonly used in [[fluid measure]] and for [[engine]] sizes.  Symbols: cm<sup>3</sup> ''and'' [[cc]]

====Translations====
*Danish: [[kubikcentimeter]] (''symbol'' cm<sup>3</sup>)
